Class FileInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • FileInfo
  • public class FileInfo
extends java.lang.Object
    Simple data structure to store file information. Synchronizes access using three separate objects for date, path, and size fields. The node set is converted to a synchronized set and must not be null or contain null values.
